# Database Rules

## Существующие таблицы (11)

| Таблица | Файл | Ключевые поля |
|---------|------|---------------|
| `users` | `schema/users.ts` | id, email, name, role (admin/editor/viewer), lastLoginAt |
| `sessions` | `schema/sessions.ts` | id, userId→users, token (SHA-256 hash), expiresAt |
| `otp_codes` | `schema/otp-codes.ts` | id, email, code (6 цифр), attempts, expiresAt, usedAt |
| `folders` | `schema/folders.ts` | id, name, parentId (self-ref), color, createdBy→users |
| `qr_codes` | `schema/qr-codes.ts` | id, shortCode, title, type, status, destinationUrl, style (JSONB), utmParams (JSONB), folderId, createdBy, totalScans, uniqueScans |
| `qr_destinations` | `schema/qr-destinations.ts` | id, qrCodeId→qr_codes, url, weight, label, clicks, isActive |
| `scan_events` | `schema/scan-events.ts` | id, qrCodeId, destinationId, ipAddress, userAgent, country, city, deviceType, os, browser, isUnique, scannedAt |
| `tags` | `schema/tags.ts` | id, name (unique), color |
| `qr_tags` | `schema/qr-tags.ts` | qrCodeId, tagId — composite PK, CASCADE |
| `allowed_domains` | `schema/allowed-domains.ts` | id, domain (unique), isActive |
| `api_keys` | `schema/api-keys.ts` | id, userId→users, name, keyHash, keyPrefix, expiresAt |

## Enums

- `user_role`: 'admin' | 'editor' | 'viewer'
- `qr_status`: 'active' | 'paused' | 'expired' | 'archived'
- `qr_type`: 'dynamic' | 'static'

## Правила создания новых таблиц

```typescript
import { pgTable, uuid, varchar, timestamp, index } from 'drizzle-orm/pg-core'

export const newTable = pgTable('new_table', {
  id: uuid('id').defaultRandom().primaryKey(),
  // ... поля ...
  createdAt: timestamp('created_at', { withTimezone: true }).defaultNow().notNull(),
}, (table) => [
  index('new_table_field_idx').on(table.fieldName),
])
```

- Все id: `uuid('id').defaultRandom().primaryKey()`
- Все timestamps: `timestamp('name', { withTimezone: true })`
- FK: `.references(() => parentTable.id, { onDelete: 'cascade' | 'set null' })`
- Добавить relations в `schema/index.ts`
- После изменения схемы: `pnpm db:generate && pnpm db:migrate`

## Relations (в schema/index.ts)

Каждая новая таблица с FK должна иметь relation definition:

```typescript
export const newTableRelations = relations(newTable, ({ one, many }) => ({
  parent: one(parentTable, {
    fields: [newTable.parentId],
    references: [parentTable.id],
  }),
  children: many(childTable),
}))
```

## DB Client

```typescript
import { db } from '../db'  // server/db/index.ts
import { tableName } from '../db/schema'  // server/db/schema/index.ts
```

Пул: max 20 соединений, idle timeout 30s.
